HEADWORD: Licker
<hw>Lick"er</hw> <pr>(l⟦icr⟧k"⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf.
<er>Lecher</er>.]</ety> <def>One who, or that which, licks.</def>⟦br⟧
